Class DQDimension

  • java.lang.Object
    • JenaDQ.DQDimension
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    _dimAccessibility, _dimCompleteness

    public abstract class DQDimension
extends java.lang.Object
    The main class of the Data Quality Model. This class can be extended overwriting the abstract methods in order to add new Data Quality Dimensions.
